==========================================================================================
                                  R E A D M E
==========================================================================================

This directory contains instructions on how to install and configure the system as well
as various files used for the look & feel or other configuration.

Directory Contents:

 * drivers: manually installed drivers --- empty at the moment.

 * instructions: install & configuration (succint) guide.

 * look-n-feel: contains various files used for Desktop appearance as well as instructions
   for the tweaks.
 
 * power-management: scripts to handle ACPI events that should trigger power management.  

 * README: this file.
 
 * udev: rules & scripts to automount removable media, etc. using udev.
